---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="IRA Forum Feedback Tips"
    description="Tips for sharing honest feedback about the IRA fee at the SJSU open forums."
>
    <main>
        <!-- Hero -->
        <section class="w-full bg-sjsublue px-6 py-16 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
            <div class="mb-6 w-full text-center mt-15">
                <h1 class="text-5xl uppercase text-white font-extrabold drop-shadow-[1.5px_1.5px_0_var(--color-auggold)]">Feedback Tips</h1>
                <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-sjsugold">
                    How to share honest feedback on the IRA fee.
                </h2>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Tips Section -->
        <section class="w-full bg-white px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
                <!-- Main Tips -->
                <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl mb-5">
                    <p class="text-base md:text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                        The IRA fee consultation process is all about honest, transparent feedback. SJSU wants to hear what you really think about the Instructionally Related Activities fee - what you like, what concerns you have, and what matters most to you. Here are some tips for sharing your perspective effectively.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        <li>
                            <span class="font-semibold">Be honest.</span> Share your genuine opinion, whether positive or critical. SJSU is listening for authentic student voices.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="font-semibold">Share your story.</span> Talk about how the fee or BayPass would affect you personally. Real examples are more powerful than abstract arguments.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="font-semibold">Be specific.</span> Instead of "it's too expensive," try "I spend $200 a month on transit fares right now." Concrete details matter.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="font-semibold">Ask questions.</span> If you're unclear about something, speak up. Your questions help SJSU understand what students need to know.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="font-semibold">Acknowledge tradeoffs.</span> If you have concerns about the fee, but also see benefits in BayPass, say that. Nuance shows you've thought about it.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="font-semibold">Keep it brief.</span> You have time to speak, but don't feel pressure to fill it all. A clear, focused comment is more effective than rambling.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-base md:text-lg mt-4 leading-relaxed">
                        Remember: SJSU is in a consultation process, not a debate. They want to understand what students think and what matters to you. Be yourself, be direct, and be honest.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Call to Action -->
                <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-clipper text-xl space-y-6">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Want to learn more?</h3>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
                            <a href="/ira" class="button flex-1 block rounded-xl font-bold bg-white px-6 py-4 font-white tracking-wide text-left">
                                What the IRA means for BayPass →
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://www.sjsu.edu/studentaffairs/proposed-ira-fee/fee-proposal.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="button flex-1 block rounded-xl font-bold bg-white px-6 py-4 font-white tracking-wide text-left">
                                What the IRA fee is →
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
